<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="A-piece" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">A-piece,</orth> to the part or share of each: <cit><quote>cost me two shilling a.</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.1.160" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 1, 160</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>sixteen businesses, a month's length a.</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 4.3.99" default="NO" valid="yes">All's IV, 3, 99</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>four bonds of forty pounds a.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.3.117" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 3, 117</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>an hundred ducats a.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 2.2.383" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. II, 2, 383</bibl></cit>.
